<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Premium Plans - GeForce APIs</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.0.0-beta1/css/all.min.css">
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@300;400;500;600;700;800;900&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <style>
        :root {
            --primary-color: #03BFCB;
            --secondary-color: #FEBB0B;
            --dark-bg: #1F1A36;
            --darker-bg: #1A162C;
            --text-color: #E0E7FF;
            --text-muted-color: #A0A8C0;
            --card-bg: #28223F;
            --border-color: #2d2747;
        }
        body {
            font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
            margin: 0;
            background-color: var(--dark-bg);
            color: var(--text-color);
            line-height: 1.7;
            padding-top: 80px; /* Space for a potential fixed header if you add one */
        }
        .container {
            width: 90%;
            max-width: 1100px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 40px 15px;
        }
        .page-header {
            text-align: center;
            margin-bottom: 50px;
        }
        .page-header h1 {
            font-size: 2.8rem;
            font-weight: 800;
            color: var(--secondary-color);
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }
        .page-header h1 i {
            margin-right: 10px;
            color: var(--primary-color);
        }
        .page-header p {
            font-size: 1.1rem;
            color: var(--text-muted-color);
            max-width: 700px;
            margin: 0 auto;
        }
        .pricing-grid {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(300px, 1fr));
            gap: 30px;
            align-items: stretch; /* Make cards same height */
        }
        .pricing-card {
            background-color: var(--card-bg);
            border-radius: 10px;
            padding: 30px;
            border: 1px solid var(--border-color);
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            text-align: center;
            transition: transform 0.3s ease, box-shadow 0.3s ease;
        }
        .pricing-card:hover {
            transform: translateY(-5px);
            box-shadow: 0 10px 30px rgba(0,0,0,0.3);
        }
        .pricing-card.popular {
            border-color: var(--primary-color);
            position: relative;
            overflow: hidden;
        }
        .popular-badge {
            position: absolute;
            top: 0;
            right: 0;
            background-color: var(--primary-color);
            color: var(--dark-bg);
            padding: 5px 15px;
            font-size: 0.8rem;
            font-weight: 600;
            transform: rotate(45deg) translate(28%, -100%);
            transform-origin: bottom left;
            width: 150px;
            text-align: center;
        }
        .pricing-card h2 {
            font-size: 1.6rem;
            font-weight: 700;
            color: var(--secondary-color);
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }
        .pricing-card .price {
            font-size: 2.5rem;
            font-weight: 800;
            color: var(--primary-color);
            margin-bottom: 5px;
        }
        .pricing-card .price span {
            font-size: 1rem;
            font-weight: 500;
            color: var(--text-muted-color);
        }
        .pricing-card .description {
            font-size: 0.9rem;
            color: var(--text-muted-color);
            margin-bottom: 25px;
            flex-grow: 1; /* Pushes button to bottom */
        }
        .pricing-card ul {
            list-style: none;
            padding: 0;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
            text-align: left;
            flex-grow: 1;
        }
        .pricing-card ul li {
            margin-bottom: 12px;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            font-size: 0.95rem;
        }
        .pricing-card ul li i {
            color: var(--primary-color);
            margin-right: 10px;
            width: 20px; /* For alignment */
        }
        .btn-select-plan {
            display: block;
            width: 100%;
            padding: 12px 20px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            font-weight: 600;
            font-size: 1rem;
            text-align: center;
            transition: background-color 0.3s ease, transform 0.2s ease;
            margin-top: auto; /* Pushes button to bottom */
            background-color: var(--primary-color);
            color: var(--dark-bg);
            border: none;
        }
        .btn-select-plan:hover {
            background-color: var(--secondary-color);
            transform: translateY(-2px);
        }
        .btn-current-plan {
            background-color: var(--border-color);
            color: var(--text-muted-color);
            cursor: default;
        }
        .btn-current-plan:hover {
            background-color: var(--border-color); /* No hover effect */
            transform: none;
        }

        .orkut-premium-section {
            background-color: var(--card-bg);
            border-radius: 10px;
            padding: 30px;
            border: 1px solid var(--border-color);
            margin-top: 50px;
            text-align: center;
        }
        .orkut-premium-section h3 {
            color: var(--secondary-color);
            font-size: 1.8rem;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
        }
        .orkut-premium-section p {
            color: var(--text-muted-color);
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }
        .orkut-premium-section .points-display {
            font-size: 1.2rem;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }
        .orkut-premium-section .points-display strong {
            color: var(--primary-color);
            font-size: 1.5rem;
        }
        .orkut-premium-section .btn-invite {
            background-color: var(--primary-color);
            color: var(--dark-bg);
            padding: 10px 25px;
            border-radius: 6px;
            font-weight: 600;
        }

        .main-footer {
            background-color: var(--darker-bg);
            padding: 30px 0;
            text-align: center;
            border-top: 1px solid var(--border-color);
            margin-top: 60px;
        }
        .main-footer p {
            margin: 0;
            font-size: 0.9rem;
            color: var(--text-muted-color);
        }
        .main-footer a {
            color: var(--primary-color);
            font-weight: 500;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="page-header">
            <h1><i class="fas fa-crown"></i>Unlock Premium Access</h1>
            <p>Choose a plan that fits your needs or earn Premium status through community engagement. Supercharge your API experience with higher limits and exclusive features!</p>
        </div>

        <div class="pricing-grid">
            <div class="pricing-card">
                <h2>Free Tier</h2>
                <div class="price">Gratis<span>/selamanya</span></div>
                <p class="description">Perfect for getting started and personal projects. Access a wide range of APIs with daily limits.</p>
                <ul>
                    <li><i class="fas fa-check-circle"></i> <%= user.dailyLimit || 50 %> Daily API Requests</li>
                    <li><i class="fas fa-check-circle"></i> Access to Standard APIs</li>
                    <li><i class="fas fa-check-circle"></i> Community Support</li>
                    <li><i class="fas fa-times-circle"></i> Higher Rate Limits</li>
                    <li><i class="fas fa-times-circle"></i> Access to Premium APIs</li>
                </ul>
                <% if (user && !user.isPremium) { %>
                    <button class="btn-select-plan btn-current-plan" disabled>Your Current Plan</button>
                <% } else { %>
                    <a href="#" class="btn-select-plan">Already on Free (or better)</a>
                <% } %>
            </div>

            <div class="pricing-card popular">
                <div class="popular-badge">Most Popular</div>
                <h2>Premium User</h2>
                <div class="price">Kontak Admin<span>/bulan</span></div>
                <p class="description">For developers and businesses requiring higher throughput and access to all features.</p>
                <ul>
                    <li><i class="fas fa-check-circle"></i> Unlimited Daily API Requests</li>
                    <li><i class="fas fa-check-circle"></i> Access to All Standard & Premium APIs</li>
                    <li><i class="fas fa-check-circle"></i> Higher Rate Limits</li>
                    <li><i class="fas fa-check-circle"></i> Priority Support</li>
                    <li><i class="fas fa-check-circle"></i> Early Access to New Features</li>
                </ul>
                 <% if (user && user.isPremium) { %>
                    <button class="btn-select-plan btn-current-plan" disabled>Your Current Plan</button>
                <% } else { %>
                    <a href="https://wa.me/6287860644193?text=Halo%20Admin%2C%20saya%20tertarik%20untuk%20upgrade%20ke%20akun%20Premium%20GeForce%20APIs." class="btn-select-plan" target="_blank">Upgrade to Premium</a>
                <% } %>
            </div>

            <div class="pricing-card">
                <h2>Community Premium</h2>
                <div class="price">Earned<span>/lifetime</span></div>
                <p class="description">Become a valued community member! Earn points by contributing, inviting friends, or participating in events.</p>
                <ul>
                    <li><i class="fas fa-check-circle"></i> Unlimited Daily API Requests</li>
                    <li><i class="fas fa-check-circle"></i> Access to All Standard & Premium APIs</li>
                    <li><i class="fas fa-check-circle"></i> Special Community Badge</li>
                    <li><i class="fas fa-star"></i> Be an Orkut Legend!</li>
                    <li><i class="fas fa-question-circle"></i> How to Earn: See Below</li>
                </ul>
                <% if (user && user.isPremium && user.earnedPremium) { %>  <!-- Add earnedPremium field to user model if distinguishing -->
                    <button class="btn-select-plan btn-current-plan" disabled>Community Premium Active</button>
                <% } else if (user && user.isPremium) { %>
                     <button class="btn-select-plan btn-current-plan" disabled>Premium Active</button>
                <% } else { %>
                     <a href="#orkut-premium" class="btn-select-plan">Learn More</a>
                <% } %>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div id="orkut-premium" class="orkut-premium-section">
            <h3><i class="fas fa-users"></i> GeForce Community Premium (Orkut Style)</h3>
            <p>We value our community! You can earn lifetime Premium access by actively participating and helping GeForce APIs grow. Here's how:</p>
            <div class="points-display">
                Your Current Points: <strong><%= user.total || 0 %> / 1000</strong> (Example target)
            </div>
            <ul>
                <li><strong>Invite Friends:</strong> Successfully invite 5 friends who actively use the API (earn 100 points each).</li>
                <li><strong>Contribute APIs:</strong> Suggest or help develop new, useful API endpoints (earn 200-500 points).</li>
                <li><strong>Bug Bounty:</strong> Report critical bugs or security vulnerabilities (earn 50-250 points).</li>
                <li><strong>Community Engagement:</strong> Actively help others in forums or Discord (points vary).</li>
            </ul>
            <p>Once you reach <strong>1000 points</strong> (example), you'll automatically be upgraded to Community Premium!</p>
            <a href="#" class="btn-invite"><i class="fas fa-share-alt mr-1"></i> Get Your Invite Link (Coming Soon)</a>
        </div>
    </div>

    <footer class="main-footer">
        <div class="container">
            <p>© <%= new Date().getFullYear() %> <a href="/">GeForce APIs</a>. All Rights Reserved.</p>
        </div>
    </footer>
</body>
</html>